snippet.title: Puzzles for Clef Trailer
snippet.description:
Puzzles for Clef is a cute and peaceful puzzle adventure with platforming elements. 

The game’s protagonist, Clef, is a young and very curious rabbit. She received a special birthday present from her sister — a treasure hunt! 

Join this charming heroine on her journey across a mysterious sky island full of unusual puzzles, eccentric locals, hidden places, and much more!

To be released on PC and Nintendo Switch in 2023.
